{"tid":1853050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚再濫用靜靜雞","createTime":"2020-01-30T17:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T20:30:26.000Z","uid":30146,"like":42,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"83af52b1397c4e097b6ca5502bb625700eff89ca","tid":1853050,"uid":30146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:51:54.000Z","msg":"唔好再靜靜雞啦 <br />\n今日元朗班文宣咪就係靜靜雞自己去貼野然後冇人知<br />\n就比鄉黑打<br />\n出去做嘢嘅講出黎 等多啲人做掩護又好乜都好<br />\n就係靜靜雞然後得小隊幾個出去<br />\n然後就冇街坊<br />\n靜靜雞係叫你班友唔好喺條街度大大聲講你去過邊！做咗啲乜！點樣走！<br />\n有啲咩威水史咪煲底先講囉！<br />\n而家公海吹雞都話要靜 唔吹雞點會有人出<br />\n一call就比人話送頭 <br />\n姐係冇人出<br />\n之後就有第二個出來笑鳩運動降溫<br />\n<br />\n吹雞都靜靜雞？咁點樣吹雞呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f8f4ea552d2004d8ab755daca33823186b9723","tid":1853050,"uid":279460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:55:23.000Z","msg":"唔好意思太多武漢PO, 借借個位黎<br />\n<br />\n721 831 721 831 721 831<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1853028/page/1#preview\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1853028/page/1#preview</a>"},{"pid":"9c157e66e1fba8db9598e26892bd6c7f04c395a6","tid":1853050,"uid":30146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3f8f4ea552d2004d8ab755daca33823186b9723","tid":1853050,"uid":279460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:55:23.000Z","msg":"唔好意思太多武漢PO, 借借個位黎<br />\n<br />\n721 831 721 831 721 831<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1853028/page/1#preview\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1853028/page/1#preview</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:56:46.000Z","msg":"今日班文宣俾鄉黑搞 721啲畫面返撚晒嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef3c45e9ee766c259b891c9c8cff812762cc2a9","tid":1853050,"uid":224657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18: